      <title>需求预期看跌挑战铁矿石价格弹性</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/bearish-demand-expectations-challenge-iron-ores-price-resilience-2024-02-28/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管中国经济前景黯淡，但铁矿石价格长期保持坚挺，但自农历新年假期结束以来，铁矿石价格大幅下跌，引发了人们对需求疲软的担忧，并削弱了澳大利亚主要生产国的矿业股。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/bearish-demand-expectations-challenge-iron-ores-price-resilience-2024-02-28/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 05:12:27 GMT</pubDate>
