      <title>香港取消房地产紧缩措施以协助经济复苏</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/hong-kong-scraps-property-tightening-measures-aid-economic-recovery-2024-02-28/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[香港财政司司长周三宣布了多项重大措施，通过取消大部分交易印花税来提振香港低迷的房地产市场，预计今年香港经济将温和增长 2.5%-3.5%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/hong-kong-scraps-property-tightening-measures-aid-economic-recovery-2024-02-28/</guid>
